{"tid":2215281,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"港「千萬富翁」50.4萬人   港每12成人1名千萬富翁    資產中位數$1700萬","createTime":"2020-09-24T01:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T04:58:34.000Z","uid":248054,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"08dd4e686a1a0ed680477e869b28cfb8d0ece265","tid":2215281,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:42:13.000Z","msg":"今年香港樓市及經濟雖面對社會事件等諸多不明朗因素，但香港千萬富翁，繼續大躍進，花旗調查發現，今年擁有千萬元資產的香港富翁達50.4萬人，千萬富翁數目較去年多22%，佔全港人口8.4%。而有逾千萬元流動資產的便有10.6萬人，按年升26%。<br />\n<br />\n&emsp;&emsp;千萬富翁的中位數是1700萬元，按年增70萬元。雖然有近八成千萬富翁看淡未來1年樓市，但花旗香港零售銀行業務主管李貴莊預計，樓價仍有半成上升空間。<br />\n<br />\n　　他指出，千萬富翁人數變動受投資情緒影響，去年底港股走勢良好，但不明朗因素較多，投資者對自身資產價格可能較為悲觀；環球大力救市下，改善投資者信心，受訪者對資產估算較樂觀。大部分千萬富翁均持有股票及人民幣資產，其次是基金、債券及貴金屬等。"},{"pid":"d2d88d425dd2cfb3760b9399164a0d28acc16a2f","tid":2215281,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:43:00.000Z","msg":"截至今年5月，2019至2020年度全港有1,000萬或以上淨資產的「千萬富翁」達50.4萬人，較2018年少7,000人，惟淨資產值中位數卻由1,630萬增至1,700萬元。受經濟影響，近8成富翁看淡未來1年樓市，但仍有1成人有意入市。有學者指，疫情對富翁資產影響較少，惟環球經濟氣氛差，料來年「走資」比例將愈來愈多。"},{"pid":"b56b9ddbe28f1666efb033264a638b14e303b37c","tid":2215281,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:43:12.000Z","msg":"7成擬送子女負笈海外 首選英國<br />\n <br />\n　　但千萬富翁的整體淨資產值中位數則由1,630萬增至1,700萬元，當中更有多達10.6萬人擁有1,000萬元或以上的流動資產，較前年的6.9萬人增逾5成，更打破自2016年以來的紀錄。<br />\n <br />\n　　調查又發現，千萬富翁淨資產總值主要分布於物業，佔高達78%，其次有10%的現金及存款、6%是股票投資等。而有79%千萬富翁坦言，看淡未來12個月的樓市，人數較去年增7個百分點，但同時仍分別有9%及13%人有興趣或認為現時是置業好時機。<br />\n <br />\n　　針對子女教育方面，7成千萬富翁有計劃送子女到海外留學，6成半以英國為留學首選，其次是澳洲及美國，各佔25%及14%。而「富翁」的子女出國年齡，平均僅15歲。"},{"pid":"36a40e1a484d9873e871d9a4aafb87f83420a00c","tid":2215281,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:43:37.000Z","msg":"香港花旗銀行零售銀行業務主管李貴莊表示，數據顯示大部分千萬富翁均持有股票、外幣及人民幣等投資工具，料他們大多以投資風險管理及多元資產平衡配置為策略，加上樓價上揚，對未來資產增加有信心，令千萬富翁淨資產中位數較2018年上升。<br />\n <br />\n中大商學院高級講師李兆波表示，疫情下的短期經濟波動一般僅影響打工仔，「有啲貨仔」的富翁通常均持一定流動現金、以及物業、股票等，投資比例傾向多元化；且今年3至5月調查期間，美股仍暢旺，樓市亦未見大變動，故即使千萬富翁數字微跌，整體資產額影響不大。<br />\n <br />\n　　但李兆波指，就目前環球經濟、中美角力持續等因素影響，料未來一年「走資」將持續急增，部分人更可能「錢走人留」等，料來年千萬富翁的人數將現跌幅，但相信不會跌破40萬人的低位。"},{"pid":"65bafabccc9500a97a6083a5b57c29b0dd292b3e","tid":2215281,"uid":28590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:43:44.000Z","msg":"港幣？美金？"},{"pid":"91d04218f9924d0595fa1fe3d20ee3c9014cf63d","tid":2215281,"uid":248054,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:44:26.000Z","msg":"樂觀易滿足 富婆開心過富翁<br />\n<br />\n調查又發現，千萬富翁的「開心指數」，若以10分為滿分，平均開心指數達6.8，且女比男開心，「富婆」高達7分，較「富翁」的6.5分高，估計是與女性較樂觀、容易滿足有關。<br />\n <br />\n　　另無育有子女或其子女已經濟獨立的富豪夫婦，開心指數更高達7.1分，較6.8分的單身貴族、及僅得6.4分、正供養子女的千萬富翁開心，反映照顧子女或令父母擁較大壓力。"},{"pid":"5dafb21d8698e904e285400dca5e22300be6d8cf","tid":2215281,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:44:40.000Z","msg":"計埋樓有邊個冇?"},{"pid":"babe997ffc7ffbc4727e347692dbd81ae332d331","tid":2215281,"uid":248054,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Krkf7Ky.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKrkf7Ky.png&h=785ca348&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3b90428e82306e4983613bd8a7b5cd3eb0db74b","tid":2215281,"uid":24335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"babe997ffc7ffbc4727e347692dbd81ae332d331","tid":2215281,"uid":248054,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Krkf7Ky.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKrkf7Ky.png&h=785ca348&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:45:43.000Z","msg":"即係收成期"},{"pid":"4f0e3b0738d500bc77437a45b6a3b78d16b9c676","tid":2215281,"uid":358248,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:48:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"550f4025b92aba81d1601b91bb48bf02994a1818","tid":2215281,"uid":374688,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:48:43.000Z","msg":"其實冇咩特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係層樓升值都賺幾百萬-過千萬啦 仲未計拎黎錢滾錢<br />\n<br />\n淨係上一兩代個班公屋廢老 大把都幾千萬身家"},{"pid":"d0f78fb01b0267327e44eeebfcfe619bfaabdfdc","tid":2215281,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:51:42.000Z","msg":"元朗屯門樓都過千萬<br />\n真係求其搭車都見到千萬富翁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba49850776af5689f4dad6e2a3ce3e19985034cd","tid":2215281,"uid":63549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:55:02.000Z","msg":"就算未到富豪級，但工作關係知道其實係香港真係好多有錢，冇經濟壓力嘅人 <br />\n呢啲中產完全同所謂靠兩公婆打工份量嗰啲<br />\n不過連燈又會話吹水大會，離地"},{"pid":"5c5f446e349b5d29183c0c351352cd0f842fe971","tid":2215281,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ba49850776af5689f4dad6e2a3ce3e19985034cd","tid":2215281,"uid":63549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:55:02.000Z","msg":"就算未到富豪級，但工作關係知道其實係香港真係好多有錢，冇經濟壓力嘅人 <br />\n呢啲中產完全同所謂靠兩公婆打工份量嗰啲<br />\n不過連燈又會話吹水大會，離地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T02:35:34.000Z","msg":"50.4萬人<br />\n當夫妻加2個小朋友<br />\n香港都有27%人係中產家庭<br />\n<br />\n事實上仲有高堂四大長老<br />\n香港真係多中產"},{"pid":"c5fb75ba40790f13361438e918ff3022992a0b89","tid":2215281,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T02:41:01.000Z","msg":"15歲 即係差唔多中1-2就扔過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc66762097f2b1cb5a5b93f0ddbf2dfc307b8b3","tid":2215281,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5fb75ba40790f13361438e918ff3022992a0b89","tid":2215281,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T02:41:01.000Z","msg":"15歲 即係差唔多中1-2就扔過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T02:46:14.000Z","msg":"中學年年都有同學走去外國讀，真係唔奇<br />\n除左英文，其他嘢外國唔難，<br />\n早去多數方便佢哋pick up英文&amp;生活"},{"pid":"55bc05982ab7c48444e7bee505996707b1fcd74f","tid":2215281,"uid":103799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T02:48:13.000Z","msg":"無可能<br />\n<br />\n香港人中位蚊人工得1萬5000蚊"},{"pid":"765d55f577ae996d995eb59e1e0fb8a2678c9207","tid":2215281,"uid":366470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T02:50:32.000Z","msg":"我有一千萬晨早移民<br />\n點解啲人會甘願留喺香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a60e52b46a12d0e446bff20a2aadd422d9a1096","tid":2215281,"uid":85584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0f78fb01b0267327e44eeebfcfe619bfaabdfdc","tid":2215281,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:51:42.000Z","msg":"元朗屯門樓都過千萬<br />\n真係求其搭車都見到千萬富翁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T02:52:35.000Z","msg":"供甩咗先計？"},{"pid":"cf161d2595c128aa78a53f4366c511e5b10fe5f9","tid":2215281,"uid":81245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"765d55f577ae996d995eb59e1e0fb8a2678c9207","tid":2215281,"uid":366470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T02:50:32.000Z","msg":"我有一千萬晨早移民<br />\n點解啲人會甘願留喺香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T02:54:35.000Z","msg":"因為有錢喺香港好住過外國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de22daecfcd645701e3264680de4dc017258953d","tid":2215281,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fc66762097f2b1cb5a5b93f0ddbf2dfc307b8b3","tid":2215281,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5fb75ba40790f13361438e918ff3022992a0b89","tid":2215281,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,